import { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import { ladiesCard, mixedCard } from "../Data"; const Card = (prop) => { const navigate = useNavigate() const [details, setDetails] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { if (prop.type == 'ladies') { setDetails(ladiesCard) } else { setDetails(mixedCard) } }, []) console.log(details) return (
{ details.map((detail) => (

{detail.statustext}

{detail.number} {detail.title}

Visit Hours

{detail.visits.visitDays}

{detail.visits.visitHours}

Services

{detail.services.inbody}

{detail.services.inbodyNo}

{detail.services.privateSessions}

{detail.services.privateSessionsNo}

{detail.services.classes}

{detail.services.classesNo}

{detail.services.invitations}

{detail.services.invitationsNo}

{detail.services.freeze}

{detail.services.freezeNo}

Price

{detail.price}EGP

)) }
) } export default Card;
